                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Tyler</persName> to <gloss type="to"
                            >acting British consul-general</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Teheran</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1898-04-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 13, 1898</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 3.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <p>Thanks for your prompt action and telegrams. Have sent in vigorous protest,
                    demanding immediate release of Bagdasarian and explanation of Emir’s
                    unjustifiable proceedings.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
